  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For a special legacy, you are returning to the island where you grew up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your family worked their entire lives for this beach. Acquired with big dreams, this beach presents an opportunity to keep their memory alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is now in your hands to take the beach to the top and transform it into an unforgettable vacation paradise for customers. However, it won't be easy. A journey full of surprises awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/c48af67d57e65ee3bbb8c975d19a9582.poster.avif?t=1728923688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/c48af67d57e65ee3bbb8c975d19a9582.webm?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/c48af67d57e65ee3bbb8c975d19a9582.mp4?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From Zero to Hero: A Magical Island Adventure</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run the first and only beach on the island! Work smart and enjoy the sea and the sand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design and develop your beach however you want with unique beach objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can design your beach sign and set regular and VIP entrance fees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can increase your popularity by valuing your customers' comments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/5aac42c87c20207a09d68c3b11508c94.poster.avif?t=1728923688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/5aac42c87c20207a09d68c3b11508c94.webm?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/5aac42c87c20207a09d68c3b11508c94.mp4?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can earn palm trees by completing level quests in the progress tab and spend them in the skills tab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can flirt with women and start a relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover treasures hidden deep in the sea with your detector! Sell your findings at auctions for the highest bid and become wealthy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize events at your desired times and design special areas. Immerse yourself in the Beach Club spirit with speakers, lighting, and a foam machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Mafia Poses the Biggest Threat to the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sea is infested with dangerous sharks that could snatch a swimming customer at any moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Criminals may infiltrate your beach and try to secretly take photos of your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your customers Could Drown In the Sea.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can either protect your beach from all these dangers or abandon it to its fate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the Apps You Need Are At Your Fingertips!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the Map app to avoid getting lost on the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place all your orders through Betrendy and wait for your delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share photos On Onstagram.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase music from Sotify and enjoy playing it on your beach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in surprise auctions or start your own with the Trader app.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track your employees and their salaries, your menu and prices, payments, and everything else related to your beach with the MyBeach app.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you earn money, you can buy luxury cars and sell them through negotiations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approaching the top, you can discover alternative ways to earn money and purchase the yacht and mansion of your dreams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/b2e33ec582b766e68f28fe315a8a6acd.poster.avif?t=1728923688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/b2e33ec582b766e68f28fe315a8a6acd.webm?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/b2e33ec582b766e68f28fe315a8a6acd.mp4?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you be able to fulfill your family's unfinished dreams?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For a special legacy, you are returning to the island where you grew up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your family worked their entire lives for this beach. Acquired with big dreams, this beach presents an opportunity to keep their memory alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is now in your hands to take the beach to the top and transform it into an unforgettable vacation paradise for customers. However, it won't be easy. A journey full of surprises awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/c48af67d57e65ee3bbb8c975d19a9582.poster.avif?t=1728923688\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/c48af67d57e65ee3bbb8c975d19a9582.webm?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2856030/extras/c48af67d57e65ee3bbb8c975d19a9582.mp4?t=1728923688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From Zero to Hero: A Magical Island Adventure</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run the first and only beach on the island! Work smart and enjoy the sea and the sand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design and develop your beach however you want with unique beach objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can design your beach sign and set regular and VIP entrance fees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can increase your popularity by valuing your customers' comments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p clas